Access code is 1212. If changed the new code will be written on a piece of paper hanging on the enterance door to the resturant upstairs. Visible from the inside. 
Restrooms are two gendered stalls, and a gender neutral handicap restroom.

Restrooms are shared with a bar in the same Building

name: Cairn Christian Church
directions: Restrooms are multi-stall and gendered, but that is only until the remodel is finished and we have a single-stall neutral facility.

name: Milagro Christian Church
directions: visible as soon as one comes in through the front door.
comment: Milagro Christian Church is an open & affirming church in the Disciples of Christ denomination (milagrocc.org). Typically there is no staff at the church during the week, so the church is only accessible on Sundays from 9:30 a.m. to approx. 12:00 noon.  The restrooms are gendered male/female and each restroom has two stalls. church mobile phone # is 719-545-6400

name: Phillips Theological Seminary
directions: There is a gender neutral bathroom in a central hallway (ask at front desk for directions). Trans men are welcome to use the men's restrooms in the building, and trans women are welcome to use the women's restrooms.
comment: Enter at the front desk and sign in to get a visitor's badge.

name: JoAnn Fabric and Crafts
directions: In the doors, all the way to the right-back in the Red Tag fabric section.  The second one is labeled unisex, but both are single-stall, locking, and accessible.

On the third floor, go to the big doors to another room (if you at a convention booths will be in that room), and look left when you find a hall, walk down and look right
If the thing open you'll see a family friendly single stall rest rooms.

name: English Landing Park
directions: Park is near farmers market shelter.  Frequently a portable potty near the shelter; in spring, summer and fall, a concrete block building inside the park.  There is a second and newer public restroom in the adjoining Platte County park, down the road to the dog runs and near the boat ramp.  Latter is open in the winter.
comment: Older restroom is closed during the winter but there will be portable potties nearby.  The newer one is open all year.
